* `condexp_convergence` - For k ‚â§ m, P[X_m ‚àà B | Œ∏_{m+1} X] = P[X_k ‚àà B | Œ∏_{m+1} X]
* `extreme_members_equal_on_tail` - P[X_m ‚àà B | tail] = P[X_0 ‚àà B | tail]

